Option                                                  Purpose
-XX:+UseSerialGC                                        Enables the Serial Garbage Collector (single-threaded).
-Xms / -Xmx                                             Sets initial and maximum heap size.
-Xlog:gc*                                               Enables detailed GC logging (Java 9+).

Run Command:
java -XX:+UseSerialGC -Xms512m -Xmx512m -Xlog:gc* com.javaPlayground.garbageCollectors.serialGC.CsvReportAnalyzer